{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/1ing.png?t=1729061650\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Jin &amp; Jan: A ghostly souls-like puzzle game with dual inverse control</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Jin &amp; Jan, </strong>in an act of<strong> </strong>mischief, splitted the world in two: the Light World and the Dark World. Now, the intrepid ghost brothers will have to bring back the balance to the world in an exciting adventure that combines <strong>puzzle and skill</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Jin follows your instructions</strong>, but his twin Jan <strong>always move to the opposite.</strong> You will need to plan every step carefully, since the enemies react to your movements: some of them move in real time and the others move as you take action.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jin and Jan will take you through increasingly difficult levels, <strong>where you will be defeated and learn</strong>. Every challenge surpassed will take you a little closer to mastering this peculiar duo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/2ing.png?t=1729061650\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mind-bending puzzles</strong>: Test your brain with puzzles that require coordination and strategic thinking. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256750/extras/V\u00eddeo_sin_t\u00edtulo_\u2010_Hecho_con_Clipchamp__1___1___1_.gif?t=1729061650\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intuitive controls</strong>: Jin &amp; Jan are easy to control, but mastering them is an art. Learn to antici